content.rendered:
Directed by Vishal Furia

Written by Mansi Bagla. Adhir Bhat. Ajit Jagtap. Vishal Kapoor

Star Radhika Apte(S.I. Megha Sharma). Vikrant Massey(Johnny Khanna). Prachi Desai. Narendra Gupta(Dr. Solanki). Rohit Roy. Vindu Dara Singh((as Vindu Singh Randhawa)). Subrat Dutta(Ved Prakash Mathur). Vishal C. Bhardwaj(Husband). Atul Vishnoi(Principal). Vidushi Manaduli(Journalist). Suneet Bora(Pant)

Language Hindi

Producers Mansi Bagla. Varun Bagla. Jatin Dharna. Deepak Mukut. Mayank Tiwari

Production Mini Films. Soham Rockstar Entertainment .Mini Films
